headline: Target (TGT): Evaluating Valuation After Recent Share Price Decline
summary: Target (TGT) in Focus as Share Price Slides: What Should Investors Watch Next? If you’ve been following Target (TGT), the recent slump in its stock price has probably raised your eyebrows.
